        For general queries, that do not need any specific context, return this: " ".s
        If you decide a file is important for the latest query, return "Check the file " +
        <full path of the file to check>.
    {{~/system}}
    {{#assistant~}}
        {{gen 'contextfile' temperature=0.0 max_tokens=500}}
    {{~/assistant}}
{{/block}}
